title: NFL Week 4 Preview
itunes:title: NFL Week 4 Preview
description:
Matt "Money" Smith and Cynthia Frelund use predictive analytics to help separate the contenders from the pretenders in the NFC East and NFC North with a game of "Stat Chat" and pick winners and fantasy football standouts for all 15 games from Sunday and Monday in Week 4 of the NFL season.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
